{"tid":292101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你唔鐘意落雨，證明你已經老了","createTime":"2017-06-21T05:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T06:05:02.000Z","uid":89622,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c82113e4bf0fd8ec138dadd129f5b4e6b4e8b3c0","tid":292101,"uid":89622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"細個嘅時候見到落雨會好開心，會特登大大力咁踩落啲水氹彈啲水去其他人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又會鳩下鳩下好似卡通片入面擋死光咁轉住把遮黎擋雨水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時候又好似星球大戰咁拎把遮左舞右舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好慶幸自己有個咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘅童年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大個咗就算出面落住雨都唔多想拎遮 見到水氹就縮都縮唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 踩到更加會忍唔住嬲爆爆咁講句：唉屌濕撚曬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BTW 落左幾日落撚夠未 對鞋入撚曬水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"9aea1d09eb3e8a7afebc1f9f2a9e54271fa005c0","tid":292101,"uid":89622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483a4f4ed005198b8fa74413a3b1d1c454c96a09","tid":292101,"uid":89622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb5fdef450e3c69ef0799530fce81a5e9c0f0cc","tid":292101,"uid":104838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:52:27.000Z","msg":"從來冇鍾意過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fc81082ca095718ec6b6412e533f50128fe862","tid":292101,"uid":89622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e10bda2f079fcfec8e928fa12dc2c5fa2fdf66f","tid":292101,"uid":89622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2dcfe1a57d01553d9d33970f57ccfcbbed002c","tid":292101,"uid":9735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"咁嘅事都要打出嚟想話畀人知你「老」了，<br />\n證明你個人仲係好幼稚"},{"pid":"a8223a6be40608d456ef4cb52bfdc39397042849","tid":292101,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"之前落雨落街買飯食<br />\n本身微微雨 遮都唔使用<br />\n無啦啦落勁撚大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我有遮就擔啦<br />\n<br />\n跟住見到條友30零歲唔攞遮 慢慢dup低頭行過 成身濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個日佢一定過得好差"},{"pid":"b8ad5ff30f93569e13a4c4965dfaf218136b23e4","tid":292101,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"以為你講緊落雨番工好撚麻煩<br />\n點知原來只係咁簡單中學生心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139bb351434564ab3c5dfcd59bb1fef780fa3659","tid":292101,"uid":89622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你講緊落雨番工好撚麻煩<br />\n點知原來只係咁簡單中學生心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返工返學都慘 仲之落雨就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}